column1:
Naming Options:\n
  1. field:[fieldname] - By Field
  2. naming_series: - By Naming Series (field called naming_series must be present
  3. Prompt - Prompt user for a name
  4. [series] - Series by prefix (separated by a dot); for example PRE.#####
    5. \n
  5. format:EXAMPLE-{MM}morewords{fieldname1}-{fieldname2}-{#####} - Replace all braced words (fieldnames, date words (DD, MM, YY), series) with their value. Outside braces, any characters can be used.
column2:
Chaguzi za jina:
  1. shamba: [shambaname] - Kwa Field
  2. Naming_series: - Kwa Naming Series (uwanja unaoitwa naming_series lazima iwepo
  3. Prompt - haraka user kwa jina
  4. [mfululizo] - Mfululizo na kiambishi (kilichotenganishwa na dot); kwa mfano PRE. #####
  5. muundo: EXAMPLE- {MM} nywila {fieldname1} - {fieldname2} - {#####} - Badilisha nafasi zote za braced (majina, maneno ya tarehe (DD, MM, YY), mfululizo) na thamani yao. Bonde la nje, wahusika wowote wanaweza kutumika.
